pull_request.title: Brand new smart fusion transformation
pull_request.body:
## Status
<!-- Choose one of the following -->
**REVIEW**

## Description
* Follow up of #470
* `ScaCPUsmartFusion` has been removed as the algorithm was not bullet-proof in real application
* `ScaCPUbasic` has been merged into `ScaCPUvectorBlock`
* New algorithm is based on the SCA CPU `single` strategy and apply various improvements: 
  * Fusion adjacent statements when possible
  * Avoid promotion of temporary used in a single vector block

## Related issues
PR #470
